query.name: findByUserIdAndStatus
query.content: SELECT t FROM TravelRequest t WHERE t.userId = :userId AND t.status = :status ORDER BY t.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findByOrgUnitNumAndEmployeeID
query.content: SELECT h FROM HpFtrFixedTermReappointmentV2 h WHERE h.orgUnitNumber = :orgUnitNumber AND h.employeeId = :employeeId

query.name: queryByVariousFields
query.content: SELECT c FROM CommonAttributes c WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and c.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:processIds IS NOT NULL and :processIds like CONCAT('%', c.processDefinitionId, '%')) OR (:processIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyType IS NOT NULL and c.partyType = :partyType) OR (:partyType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyUsername IS NOT NULL and c.partyUsername = :partyUsername) OR (:partyUsername IS NULL) ) AND ( (:status IS NOT NULL and c.status = :status) OR (:status IS NULL) ) AND ( (:caseOwnerUsername IS NOT NULL and c.caseOwnerUsername = :caseOwnerUsername) OR (:caseOwnerUsername IS NULL) ) AND ( (:enrollingUnitCode IS NOT NULL and c.enrollingUnitCode = :enrollingUnitCode) OR (:enrollingUnitCode IS NULL) ) ORDER BY c.caseId ASC

query.name: countForQueryByVariousFields
query.content: SELECT count(c) FROM CommonAttributes c WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and c.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:processIds IS NOT NULL and :processIds like CONCAT('%', c.processDefinitionId, '%')) OR (:processIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyType IS NOT NULL and c.partyType = :partyType) OR (:partyType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:partyUsername IS NOT NULL and c.partyUsername = :partyUsername) OR (:partyUsername IS NULL) ) AND ( (:status IS NOT NULL and c.status = :status) OR (:status IS NULL) ) AND ( (:caseOwnerUsername IS NOT NULL and c.caseOwnerUsername = :caseOwnerUsername) OR (:caseOwnerUsername IS NULL) ) AND ( (:enrollingUnitCode IS NOT NULL and c.enrollingUnitCode = :enrollingUnitCode) OR (:enrollingUnitCode IS NULL) )

query.name: findWWAPReqForAuditing
query.content:
SELECT requestDetails
FROM SAFAWithdrawalWithoutAcadPenV1 requestDetails
JOIN FETCH requestDetails.commonAttributes commonAttributes JOIN FETCH requestDetails.requestHistory requestEvent JOIN FETCH requestEvent.uploadedDocuments uploadedDocument
WHERE ( (:caseId IS NOT NULL and commonAttributes.caseId = :caseId) OR (:caseId IS NULL) ) AND ( (:status IS NOT NULL AND ( (:status = 'Active' AND (:activeStatuses LIKE (concat('%',commonAttributes.status,'%')))) OR (:status = 'Completed' AND (:completedStatuses LIKE (concat('%',commonAttributes.status,'%')))) ) ) OR (:status IS NULL) ) AND ( (:processIds IS NOT NULL and (:processIds LIKE (concat('%',commonAttributes.processDefinitionId,'%')))) OR (:processIds IS NULL) ) AND ( (:documentType IS NOT NULL and uploadedDocument.documentType = :documentType) OR (:documentType IS NULL) ) AND ( (:auditStatus IS NOT NULL AND ( (:auditStatus = :blankAuditStatus AND uploadedDocument.verificationStatus = null) OR uploadedDocument.verificationStatus = :auditStatus) ) OR (:auditStatus IS NULL) )
ORDER BY requestDetails.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findByEmployeeUsername
query.content: SELECT staffVaccination FROM SvStaffVaccinationV1 staffVaccination JOIN staffVaccination.employeeDetails employeeDetails WHERE :caseId IS NOT NULL AND staffVaccination.caseId <> :caseId AND :employeeUsername IS NOT NULL AND employeeDetails.employeeUsername = :employeeUsername ORDER BY staffVaccination.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findPreviousCaseFromUqMe
query.content:
SELECT sv
FROM SvStaffVaccinationV1 sv
JOIN sv.employeeDetails employeeDetails JOIN sv.currentPositionPlacementDetails currentPositionPlacementDetails JOIN currentPositionPlacementDetails.placementDetails placementDetails
WHERE sv.employeeDetails.uqme = :uqMe ORDER BY sv.caseId desc

businessObject.description: ActorMappingOverride table for Worklist Pool Routing. Stores the role and group details for tasks routed to pool from worklist. Re-evaluation of actor filter for tasks should checks this table.

query.name: findByCaseIdAndTaskIdOrderByPersistenceId
query.content: SELECT actorMappingOverride FROM ActorMappingOverride actorMappingOverride WHERE actorMappingOverride.caseId = :caseId AND actorMappingOverride.taskId = :taskId ORDER BY actorMappingOverride.persistenceId ASC

query.name: checkIfExists
query.content: SELECT s FROM SvDuplicateTableV1 s WHERE s.uqme = :uqme AND s.recallDate = :recallDate AND s.vaccinationName = :vaccinationName AND s.recallTitle = :recallTitle ORDER BY s.persistenceId ASC
